Tests fail as expected — two CS1061 errors because `RevealVaultRootCommand` doesn't exist yet. The three `BuildCommand` cross-platform tests (lines 39–59) compile fine since `FileReveal.BuildCommand` already exists, but the overall compilation fails due to the missing property. This is the correct "fail before implementation" state.

